caramel.api.objects

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • caramel.api.objects.GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Render, Update
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Prefab

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements Update, Render
    This represents a group of Components in one object. This can also contain children GameObjects.
